                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant L</hi> 6.) I received the two pieces of shilling from Mr. Hinds.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18401019-name-1392" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-1392" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18401019-name-1392" type="surname" value="GOFF"></interp>
